{"tid":561163,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"日本鐵道情報及旅遊交流區(16)","createTime":"2018-02-14T19:30:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-14T21:40:52.000Z","uid":56206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5fcd0294b60007b4314218911ffff886b429fdb9","tid":561163,"uid":56206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T19:30:55.000Z","msg":"歡迎交流日本鐵路消息及旅遊情報<br />\n有關旅遊交通(鐵路)疑難，請提供具體行程，其它人先會答到你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nJR各社Pass :<br />\nJapan Rail Pass (全國)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.japanrailpass.net/sphone/zh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.japanrailpass.net%2Fsphone%2Fzh&d=OFuqpdu9Epgjz%2B8XKCRc0BOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=0a0fcecd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.japanrailpass.net/sphone/zh</a><br />\n<br />\nJR九州Pass<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.jrkyushu.co.jp/chinese/railpass/railpass.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jrkyushu.co.jp%2Fchinese%2Frailpass%2Frailpass.jsp&d=OFuqpdu9Epgjz%2B8XKCRc0BOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=6f46b876\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.jrkyushu.co.jp/chinese/railpass/railpass.jsp</a><br />\n<br />\nJR四國Pass<br />\n<a href=\"http://shikoku-railwaytrip.com/tw/railpass.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fshikoku-railwaytrip.com%2Ftw%2Frailpass.html&d=OFuqpdu9Epgjz%2B8XKCRc0BOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=082fdb68\" target=\"_blank\">http://shikoku-railwaytrip.com/tw/railpass.html</a><br />\n<br />\nJR西日本Pass<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.westjr.co.jp/global/tc/ticket/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.westjr.co.jp%2Fglobal%2Ftc%2Fticket%2F&d=OFuqpdu9Epgjz%2B8XKCRc0BOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=95c226a7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.westjr.co.jp/global/tc/ticket/</a><br />\n<br />\nJR東海Tourist Pass<br />\n<a href=\"http://touristpass.jp/zh-tw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftouristpass.jp%2Fzh-tw&d=OFuqpdu9Epgjz%2B8XKCRc0BOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=18416516\" target=\"_blank\">http://touristpass.jp/zh-tw</a><br />\n<br />\nJR東日本Pass<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.jreast.co.jp/tc/pass/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jreast.co.jp%2Ftc%2Fpass%2Findex.html&d=OFuqpdu9Epgjz%2B8XKCRc0BOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=65e59702\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.jreast.co.jp/tc/pass/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\nJR北海道Pass<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.jrhokkaido.co.jp/global/chinese/ticket/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.jrhokkaido.co.jp%2Fglobal%2Fchinese%2Fticket%2Findex.html&d=OFuqpdu9Epgjz%2B8XKCRc0BOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=7f493c9f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.jrhokkaido.co.jp/global/chinese/ticket/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n仲有好多pass不能盡錄，詳請可以上有關鐵路公司嘅網站<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n計劃鐵路行程，可以參考哩篇&quot;日本鐵路心得&quot;<br />\n了解一啲基本概念<br />\n<a href=\"http://simontamhk.com/archives/600\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsimontamhk.com%2Farchives%2F600&d=OFuqpdu9Epgjz%2B8XKCRc0BOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=8f95e1f7\" target=\"_blank\">http://simontamhk.com/archives/600</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n常見問題FAQ：<br />\n1)xxx要點樣去？要搭幾耐先到？<br />\n你問上面路線查詢條link應該快過等人覆你<br />\n<br />\n2)去京阪神買咩pass好？<br />\n<a href=\"https://nicklee.tw/?page_id=21023\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnicklee.tw%2F%3Fpage_id%3D21023&d=OFuqpdu9Epgjz%2B8XKCRc0BOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=2e7bad1b\" target=\"_blank\">https://nicklee.tw/?page_id=21023</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bigfang.tw/blog/post/41344012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bigfang.tw%2Fblog%2Fpost%2F41344012&d=OFuqpdu9Epgjz%2B8XKCRc0BOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=26dd3078\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bigfang.tw/blog/post/41344012</a><br />\n<br />\n3)成田機埸點去/坐咩車入市區好？點買來回先平？<br />\n<a href=\"http://0rz.tw/86tRe\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F0rz.tw%2F86tRe&d=OFuqpdu9Epgjz%2B8XKCRc0BOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=c84f7f99\" target=\"_blank\">http://0rz.tw/86tRe</a><br />\n<br />\n4)點樣用JR東日本ekinet網上劃位?<br />\n<a href=\"http://amm693.wixsite.com/railway\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Famm693.wixsite.com%2Frailway&d=OFuqpdu9Epgjz%2B8XKCRc0BOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=9d6b8a95\" target=\"_blank\">http://amm693.wixsite.com/railway</a><br />\n(劃位前記得留意攞飛時限、更改或者取消劃位嘅手續費)<br />\n<br />\n有用網站<br />\n乘車記錄/里程<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.noritsubushi.org/index.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.noritsubushi.org%2Findex.php&d=OFuqpdu9Epgjz%2B8XKCRc0BOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=3931e40e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.noritsubushi.org/index.php</a><br />\n<br />\n時刻表<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ekikara.jp/top.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ekikara.jp%2Ftop.htm&d=OFuqpdu9Epgjz%2B8XKCRc0BOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=a516dada\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ekikara.jp/top.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n乗換案内<br />\n<a href=\"https://transit.yahoo.co.jp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftransit.yahoo.co.jp%2F&d=OFuqpdu9Epgjz%2B8XKCRc0BOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=2c6eece4\" target=\"_blank\">https://transit.yahoo.co.jp/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.jorudan.co.jp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jorudan.co.jp%2F&d=OFuqpdu9Epgjz%2B8XKCRc0BOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=27d3822b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.jorudan.co.jp/</a>"},{"pid":"0bccf35d2330bdf548d5723aa1e45186803680fe","tid":561163,"uid":31626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T19:34:30.000Z","msg":"唉柒咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beb8436d1d1a8d837e987ef55fc9abcf01dc55fa","tid":561163,"uid":124806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T20:52:40.000Z","msg":"有兩個16<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/face